          </def-para>
        </instrument.amend>
      </sop.para>
      <sop.para>
        <text>Definition of <emphasis style="bold">trust account</emphasis>: to insert after <quote.in quote="1">New Zealand</quote.in> (line 37 on page 75) <amend.in quote="1">or any other prescribed entity</amend.in>.</text>
